narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, Professor Simons will answer your questions instantly. Having a seminar econ intro class made it faster to find a study group too.
Would highly recommends. Professor Simons is a wonderful and patient teacher, and everyone should understand at least basic micro
